WEBVTT

00:01:35.610 --> 00:01:41.110 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.180 --> 00:01:43.710 line:80%
[Episode 25]

00:01:45.029 --> 00:01:47.360 line:80%
It wasn't easy
getting these pheasants today.

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.020 line:80%
I'll cook them later
so everyone gets some meat.

00:01:50.800 --> 00:01:52.150 line:80%
Let me handle this.

00:01:52.309 --> 00:01:53.750 line:80%
You didn't pluck the feathers clean
last time.

00:01:53.750 --> 00:01:55.480 line:80%
The brothers said what you cooked
wasn't good.

00:01:55.480 --> 00:01:56.839 line:80%
You tend the fire. Let me do it.

00:01:56.839 --> 00:01:57.440 line:80%
Okay.

00:01:57.440 --> 00:01:59.970 line:80%
You can't just use hot water
to pluck pheasant feathers.

00:01:59.970 --> 00:02:01.640 line:80%
You have to dip them in cold water first,

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:03.510 line:80%
then scald them in hot water
for half an incense stick's time.

00:02:03.510 --> 00:02:05.570 line:80%
That's the only way to get them clean.

00:02:06.590 --> 00:02:08.820 line:80%
You're quite the cook, young lady.

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:10.940 line:80%
How about this?

00:02:10.990 --> 00:02:12.320 line:80%
Come join our Mess Crew.

00:02:12.670 --> 00:02:13.990 line:80%
I can't promise much else,

00:02:13.990 --> 00:02:15.600 line:80%
but as long as we have meat to eat,

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:17.480 line:80%
you'll get a share. What do you say?

00:02:17.480 --> 00:02:18.550 line:80%
Thanks, Sir.

00:02:18.550 --> 00:02:19.670 line:80%
But I'll have to pass.

00:02:19.670 --> 00:02:21.230 line:80%
My husband is injured.

00:02:21.230 --> 00:02:22.430 line:80%
He needs someone to take care of him.

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:23.200 line:80%
Once he recovers,

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:24.320 line:80%
I'll come help right away.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:25.430 line:80%
Sure!

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:26.270 line:80%
Sure.

00:02:30.390 --> 00:02:31.200 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:02:31.990 --> 00:02:32.670 line:80%
Mr. Sun—

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:33.390 line:80%
No.

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:35.230 line:80%
Mr. Counselor,

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.640 line:80%
do you need something?

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:37.940 line:80%
Yes, I have something to tell you.

00:02:37.940 --> 00:02:38.590 line:80%
Sure.

00:02:38.830 --> 00:02:39.830 line:80%
Come, have a seat.

00:02:40.830 --> 00:02:41.480 line:80%
Thanks.

00:02:43.110 --> 00:02:45.370 line:80%
The soldiers built a new tent over there.

00:02:45.390 --> 00:02:47.080 line:80%
Yan Zheng has been moved there.

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:47.920 line:80%
Really?

00:02:48.270 --> 00:02:49.220 line:80%
It's quieter there,

00:02:49.220 --> 00:02:51.040 line:80%
so it's easier for you
to brew his medicine.

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:51.879 line:80%
That's great.

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:55.830 line:80%
But there are so many wounded.

00:02:55.830 --> 00:02:57.640 line:80%
Why move only him?

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:00.950 line:80%
Well,

00:03:01.850 --> 00:03:04.130 line:80%
in the plan to flood the bandits,

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.340 line:80%
you made a great contribution.

00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:08.260 line:80%
You even risked your life
to find your husband.

00:03:08.670 --> 00:03:10.360 line:80%
After the Marquis of Wu'an heard about it,

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:12.710 line:80%
he gave this reward
to your husband specifically.

00:03:12.710 --> 00:03:14.240 line:80%
It was only a verbal reward?

00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:15.870 line:80%
Nothing substantial?

00:03:16.990 --> 00:03:17.600 line:80%
There is!

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:22.600 line:80%
This is yours.

00:03:26.650 --> 00:03:28.629 line:80%
This isn't enough to share.

00:03:30.990 --> 00:03:32.710 line:80%
That's not it.

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:41.240 line:80%
Everyone in the pig butcher squad
has a reward.

00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:44.040 line:80%
E-Everyone?

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:46.830 line:80%
So much?

00:03:49.110 --> 00:03:50.400 line:80%
That's wonderful.

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:52.510 line:80%
A powerful noble like the Marquis of Wu'an

00:03:52.510 --> 00:03:54.080 line:80%
actually keeps us commoners

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:54.950 line:80%
in mind.

00:03:56.390 --> 00:03:57.600 line:80%
When Yan Zheng recovers,

00:03:57.600 --> 00:03:59.800 line:80%
we'll go thank him together.

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:01.200 line:80%
That won't be necessary.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:04.070 line:80%
I'll thank him properly on your behalf.

00:04:04.510 --> 00:04:05.320 line:80%
Goodbye.

00:04:10.360 --> 00:04:12.040 line:80%
I have to go find that rascal Jiuheng

00:04:12.040 --> 00:04:13.170 line:80%
to settle the score.

00:04:14.270 --> 00:04:14.710 line:80%
One!

00:04:14.830 --> 00:04:15.840 line:80%
Kill!

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:16.889 line:80%
Two!

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:18.190 line:80%
Kill!

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:18.920 line:80%
One!

00:04:18.990 --> 00:04:19.750 line:80%
Kill!

00:04:20.110 --> 00:04:20.720 line:80%
Two!

00:04:20.740 --> 00:04:21.600 line:80%
Kill!

00:04:21.629 --> 00:04:23.400 line:80%
This is the latest medicinal powder
I developed.

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:26.050 line:80%
It's great for generating body fluids
and stopping bleeding.

00:04:26.050 --> 00:04:27.320 line:80%
[Regeneration and Bleed-Stop]

00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:28.430 line:80%
I heard Your Highness
tested hundreds of herbs

00:04:28.430 --> 00:04:29.960 line:80%
to find this non-toxic one.

00:04:30.100 --> 00:04:31.560 line:80%
On behalf of the soldiers,

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:33.370 line:80%
I thank you, Your Highness.

00:04:33.400 --> 00:04:35.260 line:80%
It is my duty as a royal physician.

00:04:42.990 --> 00:04:44.990 line:80%
There is something I want to ask you.

00:04:45.070 --> 00:04:47.000 line:80%
Why are you deceiving Fan Changyu?

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:49.110 line:80%
Although she is a commoner,

00:04:49.110 --> 00:04:51.440 line:80%
I can't bear to see
such a nice lady suffer.

00:04:53.750 --> 00:04:55.600 line:80%
Except for my identity
as the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.360 line:80%
I haven't lied to her at all.

00:05:00.190 --> 00:05:01.960 line:80%
You should worry about yourself first.

00:05:01.960 --> 00:05:03.620 line:80%
Don't worry about my affairs.

00:05:04.110 --> 00:05:07.570 line:80%
Your status as the Marquis of Wu'an
is too different from hers.

00:05:08.990 --> 00:05:10.230 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an?

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:14.230 line:80%
What are you saying
about the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:05:14.230 --> 00:05:14.760 line:80%
Changyu.

00:05:15.110 --> 00:05:17.240 line:80%
Something about a status difference?

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:18.960 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:05:20.110 --> 00:05:21.370 line:80%
Did something happen?

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:25.990 line:80%
There's a status difference
between Yan Zheng

00:05:25.990 --> 00:05:27.790 line:80%
and the Marquis of Wu'an, right?

00:05:28.990 --> 00:05:30.190 line:80%
He's teaching

00:05:30.670 --> 00:05:32.800 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an
how to butter up to his wife

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:34.200 line:80%
and keep a private stash.

00:05:34.230 --> 00:05:35.430 line:80%
A private stash?

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:39.160 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
has a private stash too?

00:05:39.160 --> 00:05:40.800 line:80%
He's just like Mr. Zhao.

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:43.000 line:80%
So you must keep a close eye
on Yan Zheng.

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:45.630 line:80%
If the Marchioness finds out,

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:47.550 line:80%
he'll be in big trouble.

00:05:48.070 --> 00:05:49.230 line:80%
Seriously.

00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:51.380 line:80%
You're bad at lying to start with.

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:53.880 line:80%
Why would you give the Marquis
such an idea?

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.070 line:80%
All right.

00:05:58.070 --> 00:05:59.670 line:80%
I shan't disturb
you two lovebirds chatting.

00:05:59.670 --> 00:06:01.070 line:80%
I'm off to brew medicine.

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:05.600 line:80%
The Mess Crew caught some pheasants.

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:06.630 line:80%
I bought one

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:08.040 line:80%
to nourish your body.

00:06:10.670 --> 00:06:11.230 line:80%
Here.

00:06:21.160 --> 00:06:22.430 line:80%
It smells good.

00:06:22.990 --> 00:06:24.470 line:80%
But without salt,

00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:25.960 line:80%
it might be gamey.

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:27.750 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:35.870 line:80%
Look.

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:39.920 line:80%
What is this?

00:06:40.750 --> 00:06:42.040 line:80%
The Marquis knows about

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:44.160 line:80%
how we intercepted scouts at Baxia.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:46.400 line:80%
He rewarded me and the pig butcher squad.

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:48.459 line:80%
I have money now, so I can support you.

00:06:49.670 --> 00:06:50.520 line:80%
That's good.

00:06:52.750 --> 00:06:53.670 line:80%
By the way,

00:06:54.070 --> 00:06:57.000 line:80%
when you came up the mountain,
didn't you think about

00:06:57.070 --> 00:06:58.730 line:80%
what if you couldn't get down?

00:06:59.310 --> 00:07:00.990 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is so powerful;

00:07:00.990 --> 00:07:03.520 line:80%
he surely wouldn't let us die
on the mountain.

00:07:03.990 --> 00:07:06.590 line:80%
Even if the rebels
really attack the mountain,

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:08.110 line:80%
I can take you to escape.

00:07:09.840 --> 00:07:11.190 line:80%
If that time really comes,

00:07:11.190 --> 00:07:13.430 line:80%
just think about how to save yourself.

00:07:13.630 --> 00:07:15.040 line:80%
Why bring me along?

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:16.820 line:80%
Why not?

00:07:16.960 --> 00:07:18.420 line:80%
I said I would support you,

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.980 line:80%
and I definitely will.

00:07:24.670 --> 00:07:26.230 line:80%
When you left Lin'an,

00:07:26.630 --> 00:07:27.670 line:80%
I hit you

00:07:28.520 --> 00:07:30.160 line:80%
and said harsh words.

00:07:31.600 --> 00:07:34.000 line:80%
Every time I think about it,
I feel terrible

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:35.090 line:80%
and very guilty.

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:40.230 line:80%
You...

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.600 line:80%
You came to look for me

00:07:43.230 --> 00:07:44.890 line:80%
just because you felt guilty?

00:07:44.990 --> 00:07:46.280 line:80%
No, that's not it.

00:07:46.959 --> 00:07:47.480 line:80%
I...

00:07:48.310 --> 00:07:49.720 line:80%
I was not just guilty.

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:52.570 line:80%
You have no idea.

00:07:53.070 --> 00:07:54.290 line:80%
On my way here,

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:55.870 line:80%
I almost died.

00:07:58.670 --> 00:08:00.200 line:80%
When Lin'an was massacred,

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:02.310 line:80%
that bastard came for revenge,

00:08:02.670 --> 00:08:05.160 line:80%
and I nearly fell off a cliff to my death.

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:07.040 line:80%
Luckily,

00:08:07.230 --> 00:08:09.040 line:80%
a passing granny saved me.

00:08:11.190 --> 00:08:12.520 line:80%
I'm not afraid of death.

00:08:13.630 --> 00:08:16.760 line:80%
But I am afraid Changning
would be left without a sister.

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:20.650 line:80%
And I am afraid I'd never see you again.

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:29.070 line:80%
I missed you so much.

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:33.080 line:80%
I was so scared you were dead.

00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:35.880 line:80%
Don't die.

00:08:36.469 --> 00:08:38.430 line:80%
Come home with me, okay?

00:08:43.589 --> 00:08:44.350 line:80%
Okay.

00:09:18.590 --> 00:09:19.950 line:80%
I slept for so long.

00:09:20.310 --> 00:09:21.750 line:80%
Wake me up next time.

00:09:24.110 --> 00:09:25.300 line:80%
Sleep if you want to.

00:09:42.120 --> 00:09:42.920 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:09:44.430 --> 00:09:45.240 line:80%
Nothing.

00:09:49.070 --> 00:09:50.160 line:80%
I remember

00:09:50.640 --> 00:09:52.920 line:80%
when I brought you from the snow,

00:09:54.040 --> 00:09:56.170 line:80%
you were much dirtier than you are now.

00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:57.490 line:80%
I couldn't make out

00:09:58.280 --> 00:10:00.590 line:80%
your face with all the blood on it.

00:10:07.310 --> 00:10:07.910 line:80%
Here.

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:12.160 line:80%
Now I've nursed you back to health.

00:10:16.760 --> 00:10:18.000 line:80%
Does it still hurt?

00:10:20.040 --> 00:10:21.040 line:80%
With you here,

00:10:22.550 --> 00:10:23.550 line:80%
it's much better.

00:10:53.210 --> 00:10:53.850 line:80%
Your hand.

00:11:24.920 --> 00:11:25.880 line:80%
Changyu.

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:51.570 line:80%
You kissed me.

00:11:57.350 --> 00:11:58.350 line:80%
I...

00:11:59.670 --> 00:12:00.550 line:80%
Just now, I...

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:24.070 line:80%
Now we're even.

00:12:39.120 --> 00:12:41.120 line:80%
I'll come see you tomorrow morning.

00:12:42.430 --> 00:12:43.430 line:80%
Get some rest.

00:13:10.040 --> 00:13:11.120 line:80%
Shiny!

00:13:12.950 --> 00:13:14.400 line:80%
It's heavy.

00:13:14.400 --> 00:13:16.640 line:80%
This Marquis of Wu'an is really generous.

00:13:16.640 --> 00:13:17.160 line:80%
Here.

00:13:18.550 --> 00:13:19.470 line:80%
Boss.

00:13:19.470 --> 00:13:20.200 line:80%
Big Brother.

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:21.550 line:80%
Did you find Changyu?

00:13:22.550 --> 00:13:23.310 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:24.350 --> 00:13:25.160 line:80%
That's good.

00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:26.770 line:80%
That's good.

00:13:27.550 --> 00:13:29.680 line:80%
She found her matrilocal husband too.

00:13:29.710 --> 00:13:30.590 line:80%
Really?

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:32.040 line:80%
Look.

00:13:32.470 --> 00:13:33.310 line:80%
So much money.

00:13:40.760 --> 00:13:41.950 line:80%
Changyu is happy,

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:43.810 line:80%
so I'm happy too.

00:13:45.520 --> 00:13:46.760 line:80%
Happy, happy.

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:49.280 line:80%
I think it's our turn to get lucky.

00:13:49.520 --> 00:13:50.240 line:80%
How so?

00:13:50.350 --> 00:13:52.210 line:80%
Look, Changyu found her husband,

00:13:52.350 --> 00:13:53.670 line:80%
we got the reward money,

00:13:53.670 --> 00:13:55.520 line:80%
and there's another living soul in Lin'an.

00:13:55.520 --> 00:13:56.980 line:80%
What's that phrase again?

00:13:57.280 --> 00:13:57.950 line:80%
What phrase?

00:13:57.950 --> 00:13:59.520 line:80%
The one where everyone wins.

00:13:59.520 --> 00:14:00.350 line:80%
Everyone wins?

00:14:00.350 --> 00:14:01.550 line:80%
A win-win situation.

00:14:02.420 --> 00:14:03.020 line:80%
Right!

00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:04.430 line:80%
You're so educated.

00:14:04.430 --> 00:14:05.310 line:80%
So educated.

00:14:05.310 --> 00:14:06.070 line:80%
It didn't even come to my mind.

00:14:06.070 --> 00:14:06.470 line:80%
As expected.

00:14:06.470 --> 00:14:07.280 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:14:07.280 --> 00:14:08.920 line:80%
-Big Bro will definitely succeed
-What's with the noise?

00:14:08.920 --> 00:14:11.120 line:80%
Are you going to let people sleep or not?

00:14:12.040 --> 00:14:13.870 line:80%
Why... Why is it you guys again?

00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:15.280 line:80%
It's you again, isn't it?

00:14:15.280 --> 00:14:15.950 line:80%
Come back.

00:14:22.650 --> 00:14:23.320 line:80%
Go back.

00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:35.400 line:80%
Come on. Cheers.

00:14:36.860 --> 00:14:38.260 line:80%
Come on. Cheers.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:46.890 line:80%
Here.

00:14:57.830 --> 00:14:58.760 line:80%
Changyu.

00:15:17.630 --> 00:15:20.570 line:80%
Sister, I'm cold.

00:15:21.310 --> 00:15:21.950 line:80%
Here.

00:15:23.480 --> 00:15:24.240 line:80%
Cover up.

00:16:01.280 --> 00:16:02.650 line:80%
He's so badly injured.

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:06.290 line:80%
How can he still go to the battlefield?

00:16:19.800 --> 00:16:22.590 line:80%
I'm freezing to death.

00:16:27.640 --> 00:16:30.170 line:80%
She might as well sleep with Brother-in-Law.

00:16:35.920 --> 00:16:39.150 line:80%
[Xie]

00:16:44.510 --> 00:16:45.480 line:80%
Counselor!

00:16:47.590 --> 00:16:48.240 line:80%
Her High—

00:16:48.640 --> 00:16:50.240 line:80%
The Royal Physician, she...

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:51.190 line:80%
What happened to her?

00:16:51.190 --> 00:16:52.000 line:80%
Quick!

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:02.860 line:80%
Your Highness!

00:17:16.869 --> 00:17:20.600 line:80%
Jianjia, this prescription
works wonders for internal injuries.

00:17:21.240 --> 00:17:23.629 line:80%
Distribute it
to the other medics immediately.

00:17:23.629 --> 00:17:25.240 line:80%
Tell them to brew it at once.

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:35.510 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:17:37.150 --> 00:17:38.960 line:80%
Just to fiddle with these herbs,

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:41.590 line:80%
you ruin your health?

00:17:42.630 --> 00:17:44.170 line:80%
I've tested them myself.

00:17:44.910 --> 00:17:46.440 line:80%
These herbs are non-toxic

00:17:46.590 --> 00:17:48.190 line:80%
and can be found everywhere.

00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:49.310 line:80%
You...

00:17:50.550 --> 00:17:51.870 line:80%
You tested the medicine yourself?

00:17:51.870 --> 00:17:54.470 line:80%
Her Highness has tested many kinds.

00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:56.610 line:80%
She's almost lost her sense of taste.

00:17:56.960 --> 00:17:58.590 line:80%
There's no salt in the army anyway.

00:17:58.590 --> 00:17:59.680 line:80%
It's just as well.

00:18:00.070 --> 00:18:02.200 line:80%
It saves me from tasting the gaminess.

00:18:04.760 --> 00:18:05.630 line:80%
The medicine is ready.

00:18:05.630 --> 00:18:06.680 line:80%
Go, Jianjia.

00:18:11.960 --> 00:18:13.390 line:80%
As the Princess Royal,

00:18:13.800 --> 00:18:15.000 line:80%
you are incredibly noble.

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:17.080 line:80%
How can you be so reckless?

00:18:17.240 --> 00:18:18.700 line:80%
I am a royal physician now.

00:18:19.040 --> 00:18:21.350 line:80%
I came to this army to save people.

00:18:21.480 --> 00:18:23.800 line:80%
Fine, even if you are a physician,

00:18:23.830 --> 00:18:25.310 line:80%
the origin of these herbs is unknown.

00:18:25.310 --> 00:18:26.520 line:80%
What if they are poisonous?

00:18:26.520 --> 00:18:28.440 line:80%
-It can be fatal.
-So what?

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:29.870 line:80%
I told you,

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:32.740 line:80%
don't treat me as the Princess Royal.

00:18:33.390 --> 00:18:35.960 line:80%
Headmaster,
you are not a teacher at the academy here.

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:38.220 line:80%
In what capacity are you questioning me?

00:18:40.800 --> 00:18:41.760 line:80%
Back at the academy,

00:18:41.760 --> 00:18:43.350 line:80%
didn't you say,

00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:48.040 line:80%
"A ruler must bear the burden
of protecting the common people"?

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:52.720 line:80%
A ruler must bear the burden
of protecting the common people.

00:18:53.120 --> 00:18:54.490 line:80%
A ruler of a nation

00:18:54.520 --> 00:18:56.240 line:80%
must shoulder the heavy responsibility

00:18:56.240 --> 00:18:58.870 line:80%
of protecting the people of the world.

00:19:01.720 --> 00:19:03.980 line:80%
That is the way of the ruler and minister.

00:19:04.280 --> 00:19:06.440 line:80%
The Princess Royal is of noble birth

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:08.200 line:80%
and a woman.

00:19:09.520 --> 00:19:11.240 line:80%
Why be so harsh on yourself?

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:16.920 line:80%
Precisely because I bear the duties
of the Princess Royal

00:19:17.000 --> 00:19:19.130 line:80%
and enjoy the blessings of the people,

00:19:19.480 --> 00:19:23.080 line:80%
I have even more responsibility
and obligation to protect them.

00:19:23.390 --> 00:19:24.240 line:80%
Don't I?

00:19:37.680 --> 00:19:38.800 line:80%
This way,

00:19:39.150 --> 00:19:41.310 line:80%
the soldiers' pain can be alleviated,

00:19:42.200 --> 00:19:43.330 line:80%
and for this battle,

00:19:44.310 --> 00:19:45.960 line:80%
there is hope of winning.

00:19:57.280 --> 00:19:59.280 line:80%
Your Highness, drink the medicine.

00:20:00.680 --> 00:20:01.480 line:80%
What's this?

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:04.070 line:80%
Her Highness tests herbs daily,
so being poisoned is inevitable.

00:20:04.070 --> 00:20:07.400 line:80%
This is the antidote soup
Her Highness prepared in advance.

00:20:07.410 --> 00:20:08.200 line:80%
Let me.

00:20:14.200 --> 00:20:14.830 line:80%
It seems

00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:16.600 line:80%
you're not stupid after all.

00:20:17.310 --> 00:20:19.840 line:80%
You knew to prepare
an antidote for yourself.

00:20:24.280 --> 00:20:24.830 line:80%
Here.

00:20:26.070 --> 00:20:27.600 line:80%
Who are you calling stupid?

00:20:31.110 --> 00:20:31.830 line:80%
I'm stupid.

00:20:33.390 --> 00:20:34.000 line:80%
Here.

00:20:34.910 --> 00:20:36.240 line:80%
I'm stupid, I'm stupid.

00:20:37.070 --> 00:20:37.900 line:80%
Slowly.

00:20:48.350 --> 00:20:50.110 line:80%
That wretched girl
who delivered the grain,

00:20:50.110 --> 00:20:50.960 line:80%
she's the dame the Heir Apparent ordered

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:52.160 line:80%
to be captured alive.

00:20:53.910 --> 00:20:56.110 line:80%
This dame is not simple.

00:20:56.800 --> 00:20:58.460 line:80%
She killed three of our scouts

00:20:58.480 --> 00:21:00.480 line:80%
and even stabbed the Heir Apparent.

00:21:01.390 --> 00:21:03.960 line:80%
She's ruthless and incredibly bold.

00:21:04.110 --> 00:21:06.550 line:80%
If I'd known, I would have ambushed
that grain convoy myself.

00:21:06.550 --> 00:21:08.830 line:80%
I missed a good chance
to earn merit for nothing.

00:21:08.830 --> 00:21:09.870 line:80%
Hu.

00:21:09.870 --> 00:21:11.110 line:80%
Remember this.

00:21:11.350 --> 00:21:13.520 line:80%
As long as the Heir Apparent
is in their hands,

00:21:13.520 --> 00:21:15.630 line:80%
we cannot act rashly.

00:21:15.830 --> 00:21:17.390 line:80%
How long must we swallow this till?

00:21:17.390 --> 00:21:18.480 line:80%
The Old Prince is still waiting for us

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:19.680 line:80%
to meet up in Lucheng!

00:21:19.870 --> 00:21:22.000 line:80%
Of course we won't swallow it forever.

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:24.540 line:80%
But to deal with the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:21:24.800 --> 00:21:26.240 line:80%
we have to outsmart them.

00:21:26.760 --> 00:21:28.820 line:80%
A brute attack will only end in a loss.

00:21:34.200 --> 00:21:36.660 line:80%
Let's surround them
and break their spirit.

00:21:36.760 --> 00:21:38.480 line:80%
Once their army morale crumbles,

00:21:38.480 --> 00:21:40.340 line:80%
we'll seize the chance to attack.

00:21:41.200 --> 00:21:42.040 line:80%
But what about the Heir Apparent's safety—

00:21:42.040 --> 00:21:44.960 line:80%
We have to wait for the Marquis of Wu'an
to lower his guard;

00:21:44.960 --> 00:21:47.310 line:80%
only then can we rescue the Heir Apparent.

00:21:57.070 --> 00:21:57.520 line:80%
Hurry.

00:21:58.070 --> 00:21:58.550 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:21:58.550 --> 00:22:00.350 line:80%
Why are we gathering so early?

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:03.330 line:80%
Do you smell that aroma?

00:22:04.070 --> 00:22:05.530 line:80%
It smells like roast meat.

00:22:13.070 --> 00:22:14.320 line:80%
Give me a piece.

00:22:14.630 --> 00:22:16.200 line:80%
It smells so good.

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:18.480 line:80%
It's been ages since I had meat.

00:22:18.480 --> 00:22:19.150 line:80%
Roast meat?

00:22:19.150 --> 00:22:20.280 line:80%
Where is it? Find it.

00:22:20.440 --> 00:22:21.200 line:80%
Where?

00:22:22.070 --> 00:22:22.830 line:80%
Here.

00:22:26.090 --> 00:22:27.020 line:80%
[Regeneration and Bleed-Stop]

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:32.070 line:80%
Jiu—

00:22:34.590 --> 00:22:35.480 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:22:35.550 --> 00:22:37.110 line:80%
Come in. No one's here.

00:22:39.550 --> 00:22:40.720 line:80%
Good news.

00:22:41.960 --> 00:22:43.310 line:80%
After you asked the soldiers
at the foot of the mountain

00:22:43.310 --> 00:22:44.670 line:80%
to scrape tree bark and dig tree roots,

00:22:44.670 --> 00:22:46.070 line:80%
they really fell for the trap.

00:22:46.070 --> 00:22:48.590 line:80%
They all thought we're out of food
in the mountain.

00:22:48.590 --> 00:22:51.350 line:80%
Now, to the east and south of the hill,

00:22:51.350 --> 00:22:52.680 line:80%
they're roasting lamb.

00:22:52.680 --> 00:22:55.480 line:80%
and want to dampen our soldiers' morale
with that.

00:22:55.480 --> 00:22:57.280 line:80%
Shi Yue is pretty smart

00:22:57.830 --> 00:22:59.200 line:80%
for thinking of that.

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:01.040 line:80%
They're underestimating us.

00:23:01.040 --> 00:23:03.320 line:80%
The men of Yanzhou have backbone.

00:23:04.150 --> 00:23:05.720 line:80%
Even if we didn't have food,

00:23:05.800 --> 00:23:07.540 line:80%
and had to eat roots and bark,

00:23:07.570 --> 00:23:08.760 line:80%
we wouldn't surrender to those rebels

00:23:08.760 --> 00:23:10.200 line:80%
because of such cheap tricks.

00:23:10.200 --> 00:23:12.520 line:80%
He has brains, but not much.

00:23:12.760 --> 00:23:13.720 line:80%
Exactly.

00:23:16.430 --> 00:23:17.560 line:80%
Proceed as planned.

00:23:18.350 --> 00:23:19.550 line:80%
-Yes, Sir.
-Yes, Sir.

00:23:25.720 --> 00:23:28.120 line:80%
Where is that roast meat smell
coming from?

00:23:35.590 --> 00:23:36.800 line:80%
Hurry up, hurry.

00:23:47.040 --> 00:23:47.800 line:80%
Sir.

00:23:48.040 --> 00:23:51.170 line:80%
Do you know where the men
from the light injury camp went?

00:23:51.560 --> 00:23:52.970 line:80%
The rebels are roasting lamb
down the hill.

00:23:52.970 --> 00:23:54.210 line:80%
The whole camp is on alert.

00:23:54.210 --> 00:23:56.070 line:80%
Those in the light injury camp...

00:23:56.070 --> 00:23:58.000 line:80%
must have been summoned urgently.

00:24:00.440 --> 00:24:02.040 line:80%
They've gone to fight again?

00:24:02.050 --> 00:24:03.980 line:80%
Their wounds haven't even healed.

00:24:06.910 --> 00:24:07.630 line:80%
Sir.

00:24:08.070 --> 00:24:10.330 line:80%
Do you know where they are going to fight?

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:10.960 line:80%
I don't.

00:24:10.960 --> 00:24:12.550 line:80%
Prying into military secrets

00:24:12.550 --> 00:24:13.750 line:80%
can get you beheaded.

00:24:15.290 --> 00:24:17.790 line:80%
I'm just worried about Yan Zheng's injury.

00:24:19.720 --> 00:24:21.520 line:80%
Your husband is capable.

00:24:21.520 --> 00:24:22.580 line:80%
He's very skilled.

00:24:22.830 --> 00:24:23.760 line:80%
He'll be fine.

00:24:24.520 --> 00:24:26.050 line:80%
No matter how skilled he is,

00:24:26.340 --> 00:24:27.750 line:80%
he's just a foot soldier.

00:24:28.390 --> 00:24:30.520 line:80%
He'll always be on the front lines.

00:24:34.280 --> 00:24:36.830 line:80%
Even if the Marquis of Wu'an
is on the front lines,

00:24:36.830 --> 00:24:38.520 line:80%
it's to protect everyone.

00:24:44.830 --> 00:24:47.490 line:80%
Then I hope the Marquis of Wu'an
can protect him.

00:24:51.280 --> 00:24:52.350 line:80%
Changyu!

00:24:54.240 --> 00:24:55.240 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:24:55.630 --> 00:24:56.910 line:80%
The cave...

00:25:00.240 --> 00:25:01.280 line:80%
In the cave...

00:25:01.550 --> 00:25:03.480 line:80%
What about the cave? Speak slowly.

00:25:04.150 --> 00:25:05.960 line:80%
That villain,

00:25:06.150 --> 00:25:09.000 line:80%
I saw him get caught.

00:25:09.000 --> 00:25:11.060 line:80%
They locked him in the cave.

00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:15.900 line:80%
Take care of Changning for me.

00:25:17.830 --> 00:25:20.000 line:80%
Changning, who is this villain?

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:21.040 line:80%
What did he do?

00:25:21.110 --> 00:25:25.560 line:80%
I saw him killing people in Xigu Lane.

00:25:31.280 --> 00:25:32.230 line:80%
Important prisoners are held here.

00:25:32.230 --> 00:25:33.630 line:80%
No trespassing allowed.

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:35.800 line:80%
I just want to know

00:25:36.110 --> 00:25:37.040 line:80%
if the one inside

00:25:37.800 --> 00:25:39.820 line:80%
is that bastard named Sui.

00:25:40.440 --> 00:25:42.920 line:80%
Is that Mrs. Fan out there?

00:25:43.390 --> 00:25:44.830 line:80%
To think you'd come here.

00:25:48.200 --> 00:25:50.630 line:80%
Our fate is indeed destined by heaven.

00:25:50.910 --> 00:25:52.390 line:80%
Did you come to catch up with me?

00:25:52.390 --> 00:25:53.630 line:80%
I'll kill you right now, you bastard!

00:25:53.630 --> 00:25:54.200 line:80%
Military orders are absolute.

00:25:54.200 --> 00:25:54.910 line:80%
Do not make a mistake.

00:25:54.910 --> 00:25:55.910 line:80%
I don't care about your orders.

00:25:55.910 --> 00:25:56.830 line:80%
My mother is dead.

00:25:56.830 --> 00:25:58.070 line:80%
Why should he live?

00:25:58.280 --> 00:25:58.870 line:80%
Wait!

00:26:01.550 --> 00:26:02.520 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:26:03.070 --> 00:26:04.690 line:80%
I know why you are here.

00:26:04.830 --> 00:26:06.200 line:80%
But the prisoner held here

00:26:06.200 --> 00:26:07.800 line:80%
is crucial to the entire war.

00:26:07.900 --> 00:26:09.910 line:80%
He is a risky pawn to check the enemy.

00:26:10.040 --> 00:26:11.350 line:80%
He can't die yet.

00:26:11.910 --> 00:26:13.640 line:80%
I just want to ask him one thing.

00:26:14.830 --> 00:26:16.690 line:80%
Why did he slaughter Lin'an Town?

00:26:18.110 --> 00:26:19.630 line:80%
Those innocent people...

00:26:20.760 --> 00:26:22.480 line:80%
what crime did they commit?

00:26:24.070 --> 00:26:25.580 line:80%
Then come in.

00:26:26.440 --> 00:26:27.950 line:80%
Come in and I'll tell you.

00:26:27.990 --> 00:26:28.760 line:80%
I'll kill you.

00:26:28.760 --> 00:26:29.240 line:80%
Fine!

00:26:31.680 --> 00:26:33.740 line:80%
But only you can come in with me alone.

00:26:34.000 --> 00:26:35.000 line:80%
Give me the sword.

00:27:01.000 --> 00:27:01.680 line:80%
Open the door.

00:27:01.680 --> 00:27:02.150 line:80%
Yes.

00:27:08.760 --> 00:27:11.280 line:80%
We meet again
before the blood has even dried.

00:27:11.280 --> 00:27:12.200 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:27:12.630 --> 00:27:14.830 line:80%
I've been thinking about you every day.

00:27:15.240 --> 00:27:16.100 line:80%
What about you?

00:27:16.720 --> 00:27:18.070 line:80%
Did you miss me?

00:27:20.000 --> 00:27:21.130 line:80%
I miss you so much...

00:27:22.680 --> 00:27:24.810 line:80%
that I want you to die a horrible death.

00:27:28.680 --> 00:27:30.720 line:80%
Why did you massacre Lin'an?

00:27:33.550 --> 00:27:34.870 line:80%
Why?

00:27:36.240 --> 00:27:37.390 line:80%
For no reason.

00:27:38.280 --> 00:27:40.630 line:80%
Didn't Xie Zheng want to protect Lin'an?

00:27:41.150 --> 00:27:43.150 line:80%
I just wouldn't let him have his way.

00:27:43.960 --> 00:27:45.720 line:80%
Anyone from Lin'an

00:27:46.720 --> 00:27:48.350 line:80%
must die.

00:27:52.440 --> 00:27:54.150 line:80%
Just out of spite?

00:27:56.310 --> 00:27:58.640 line:80%
The old, the weak, women, and children...

00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:01.000 line:80%
you didn't spare a single one.

00:28:02.680 --> 00:28:04.630 line:80%
They were just ants.

00:28:07.630 --> 00:28:09.150 line:80%
Are you that angry?

00:28:09.260 --> 00:28:10.830 line:80%
Then let me tell you more.

00:28:10.830 --> 00:28:12.070 line:80%
Your sister,

00:28:12.440 --> 00:28:13.720 line:80%
the little girl

00:28:14.240 --> 00:28:15.960 line:80%
with Tuberculosis.

00:28:16.630 --> 00:28:18.440 line:80%
When I forced her to ride in front of me,

00:28:18.440 --> 00:28:19.510 line:80%
she couldn't stand the bumps,

00:28:19.510 --> 00:28:20.570 line:80%
she kept vomiting,

00:28:20.960 --> 00:28:22.680 line:80%
I almost drowned her in the water.

00:28:22.680 --> 00:28:24.350 line:80%
The look on her face...

00:28:25.110 --> 00:28:26.800 line:80%
was so entertaining.

00:28:30.630 --> 00:28:32.000 line:80%
And that darn constable.

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:33.110 line:80%
He was so stubborn!

00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:36.870 line:80%
But he still died with one stab from me.

00:28:38.800 --> 00:28:40.590 line:80%
As for the magistrate's daughter,

00:28:40.590 --> 00:28:42.720 line:80%
she refused to tell me where you were.

00:28:42.720 --> 00:28:43.870 line:80%
I showed no mercy.

00:28:43.870 --> 00:28:45.110 line:80%
With one thrust of my spear,

00:28:45.110 --> 00:28:47.310 line:80%
her blood sprayed 3 chi high.

00:28:58.440 --> 00:28:59.200 line:80%
Mrs. Fan!

00:28:59.200 --> 00:28:59.870 line:80%
Calm down!

00:28:59.870 --> 00:29:00.480 line:80%
Come on!

00:29:00.910 --> 00:29:01.830 line:80%
Do it!

00:29:01.960 --> 00:29:03.040 line:80%
Kill me!

00:29:06.910 --> 00:29:07.910 line:80%
Mrs. Fan!

00:30:00.910 --> 00:30:02.510 line:80%
Your Lordship, bad news.

00:30:02.910 --> 00:30:05.110 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing was taken away by Mrs. Fan.

00:30:07.800 --> 00:30:09.680 line:80%
If you have the guts, make it quick.

00:30:09.680 --> 00:30:10.870 line:80%
Just kill me now!

00:30:11.590 --> 00:30:13.310 line:80%
I won't let you off that easily.

00:30:13.310 --> 00:30:15.200 line:80%
You bunch of cowards.

00:30:15.440 --> 00:30:17.070 line:80%
Think you can avenge the people of Lin'an?

00:30:17.070 --> 00:30:17.830 line:80%
One more word,

00:30:17.830 --> 00:30:19.690 line:80%
and I'll slaughter you right now.

00:30:21.200 --> 00:30:22.110 line:80%
His Lordship arranged this.

00:30:22.110 --> 00:30:23.110 line:80%
Just watch.

00:30:23.110 --> 00:30:24.110 line:80%
Let me go!

00:30:25.390 --> 00:30:26.320 line:80%
Tie him tighter.

00:30:28.150 --> 00:30:28.800 line:80%
Done.

00:30:30.200 --> 00:30:31.280 line:80%
Bandits!

00:30:32.310 --> 00:30:34.350 line:80%
Open your dog eyes and look!

00:30:34.910 --> 00:30:36.480 line:80%
Your Heir Apparent

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:38.480 line:80%
is in my hands!

00:30:39.550 --> 00:30:40.350 line:80%
Sir,

00:30:40.630 --> 00:30:41.830 line:80%
it really is the Heir.

00:30:42.110 --> 00:30:43.310 line:80%
Should we save him?

00:30:46.800 --> 00:30:47.400 line:80%
That is...

00:30:48.870 --> 00:30:50.160 line:80%
Mrs. Fan?

00:30:51.200 --> 00:30:52.110 line:80%
Ridiculous.

00:30:52.680 --> 00:30:55.790 line:80%
Could Xie Zheng have seen through my plan?

00:30:56.550 --> 00:30:57.240 line:80%
Sir,

00:30:57.520 --> 00:30:58.960 line:80%
why don't we charge up the mountain

00:30:58.960 --> 00:30:59.890 line:80%
and save the Heir

00:31:00.040 --> 00:31:01.200 line:80%
first?

00:31:01.200 --> 00:31:01.910 line:80%
No.

00:31:02.870 --> 00:31:05.070 line:80%
Xie Zheng might be plotting something.

00:31:05.750 --> 00:31:06.900 line:80%
I'll take a squad

00:31:07.110 --> 00:31:08.770 line:80%
and check the west side first.

00:31:09.110 --> 00:31:11.310 line:80%
You stay here and keep luring the enemy.

00:31:11.480 --> 00:31:12.440 line:80%
Sound the horn.

00:31:13.350 --> 00:31:14.210 line:80%
Sound the horn!

00:31:25.350 --> 00:31:27.760 line:80%
What? Scared now?

00:31:28.310 --> 00:31:29.970 line:80%
If you're scared, let me down.

00:31:30.440 --> 00:31:32.000 line:80%
When my army comes up,

00:31:32.590 --> 00:31:34.520 line:80%
I might leave your corpses intact.

00:31:43.870 --> 00:31:44.520 line:80%
Look.

00:31:45.040 --> 00:31:46.170 line:80%
Shi Yue moved first.

00:31:46.590 --> 00:31:48.450 line:80%
Why did he only take a small group?

00:31:49.350 --> 00:31:50.590 line:80%
What is he doing?

00:31:53.240 --> 00:31:55.000 line:80%
To the north of this place is mountains,

00:31:55.000 --> 00:31:56.680 line:80%
and the other 3 sides
are surrounded by wilderness.

00:31:56.680 --> 00:31:58.520 line:80%
The west is clearly upwind,

00:31:59.310 --> 00:32:00.550 line:80%
yet he ordered his men

00:32:01.040 --> 00:32:03.570 line:80%
to roast meat
only on the south and east sides.

00:32:04.350 --> 00:32:06.610 line:80%
It seems he wants to demoralize us first,

00:32:07.720 --> 00:32:09.110 line:80%
and then he has another move planned

00:32:09.110 --> 00:32:11.110 line:80%
to lure the tiger from the mountain.

00:32:11.480 --> 00:32:12.280 line:80%
He wants us to step into

00:32:12.280 --> 00:32:14.110 line:80%
his carefully laid trap.

00:32:15.110 --> 00:32:16.310 line:80%
He's got some brains.

00:32:19.720 --> 00:32:21.440 line:80%
So you're the Heir Apparent?

00:32:23.870 --> 00:32:25.580 line:80%
This is for my grandma.

00:32:26.070 --> 00:32:27.240 line:80%
Peasant.

00:32:27.350 --> 00:32:28.290 line:80%
How dare you—

00:32:28.760 --> 00:32:30.350 line:80%
If not for you little bastard,

00:32:30.350 --> 00:32:31.950 line:80%
my mother wouldn't be paralyzed in bed.

00:32:31.950 --> 00:32:33.390 line:80%
You scared her paralyzed.

00:32:33.390 --> 00:32:34.720 line:80%
I wanted to go back in glory,

00:32:34.720 --> 00:32:35.720 line:80%
stay by her side,

00:32:35.720 --> 00:32:37.590 line:80%
and be there for her end.

00:32:37.830 --> 00:32:38.870 line:80%
Is there no end?

00:32:39.800 --> 00:32:41.460 line:80%
My little sister is crippled.

00:32:41.590 --> 00:32:43.920 line:80%
She should have had a better life.

00:32:43.970 --> 00:32:45.240 line:80%
Because of you,

00:32:45.240 --> 00:32:46.630 line:80%
her life is ruined.

00:32:46.630 --> 00:32:47.760 line:80%
Is there no end?

00:32:48.040 --> 00:32:49.040 line:80%
Enough!

00:32:50.110 --> 00:32:51.830 line:80%
What did we people of Lin'an do wrong?

00:32:51.830 --> 00:32:54.030 line:80%
You didn't even give us a chance to live!

00:32:56.590 --> 00:32:58.390 line:80%
Pigs want to live too.

00:32:59.040 --> 00:33:00.200 line:80%
What's the use?

00:33:01.800 --> 00:33:03.860 line:80%
They still get slaughtered for meat.

00:33:03.910 --> 00:33:05.200 line:80%
You lot

00:33:06.350 --> 00:33:08.110 line:80%
can't even be compared to a pig.

00:33:10.590 --> 00:33:12.370 line:80%
You want to die, right?

00:33:12.440 --> 00:33:13.500 line:80%
Let me handle this.

00:33:18.110 --> 00:33:19.860 line:80%
This stunt your wife is pulling

00:33:19.960 --> 00:33:22.240 line:80%
probably has Shi Yue all on edge.

00:33:22.680 --> 00:33:24.910 line:80%
He won't be able to come up
with any clever moves.

00:33:24.910 --> 00:33:25.970 line:80%
It's reckless,

00:33:26.070 --> 00:33:27.870 line:80%
but it hit the mark by sheer luck.

00:33:28.390 --> 00:33:30.250 line:80%
Shi Yue is naturally suspicious.

00:33:30.760 --> 00:33:33.560 line:80%
Seeing this,
he'll surely keep the main army back,

00:33:34.070 --> 00:33:35.910 line:80%
and lead a small squad for a raid himself,

00:33:35.910 --> 00:33:38.640 line:80%
waiting for a chance
to come up to get him himself.

00:33:40.350 --> 00:33:41.150 line:80%
Come on.

00:33:41.590 --> 00:33:42.550 line:80%
Hit me.

00:33:42.960 --> 00:33:44.390 line:80%
I like being hit by you.

00:33:47.390 --> 00:33:48.240 line:80%
Hit you?

00:33:49.440 --> 00:33:51.000 line:80%
That's letting you off too easy.

00:33:51.000 --> 00:33:51.960 line:80%
Gag him.

00:33:54.070 --> 00:33:54.930 line:80%
I'll do it.

00:33:55.910 --> 00:33:57.630 line:80%
I haven't bathed in 5 days anyway.

00:33:57.630 --> 00:33:58.680 line:80%
It's just a bit smelly.

00:33:58.680 --> 00:33:59.480 line:80%
Give me a hand.

00:34:01.110 --> 00:34:01.770 line:80%
Don't move.

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:02.480 line:80%
Stay still.

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:03.540 line:80%
Stop moving.

00:34:10.030 --> 00:34:11.200 line:80%
Rebels!

00:34:12.200 --> 00:34:14.800 line:80%
If you want to keep
your Heir Apparent alive,

00:34:15.760 --> 00:34:17.830 line:80%
you must trade meat and food for it!

00:34:24.510 --> 00:34:25.970 line:80%
They don't seem to hear us.

00:34:31.160 --> 00:34:34.720 line:80%
If you want to save
your Heir Apparent's life,

00:34:34.720 --> 00:34:37.280 line:80%
bring salt and meat!

00:34:39.950 --> 00:34:41.990 line:80%
I'm good at foreseeing things,

00:34:41.990 --> 00:34:43.430 line:80%
but I really cannot figure

00:34:43.430 --> 00:34:44.910 line:80%
your wife out.

00:34:47.950 --> 00:34:49.080 line:80%
Xie Wu, Xie Qi.

00:34:49.430 --> 00:34:50.760 line:80%
Stay here with me.

00:34:50.830 --> 00:34:51.600 line:80%
Xie Jiu.

00:34:51.950 --> 00:34:53.870 line:80%
Go with the strategist
to reinforce them immediately.

00:34:53.870 --> 00:34:54.640 line:80%
Yes, Sir.

00:34:54.930 --> 00:34:58.360 line:80%
Ignoring us, huh? I'll whip you to death.

00:35:00.470 --> 00:35:01.730 line:80%
Is that all you've got?

00:35:03.560 --> 00:35:05.120 line:80%
You've been collecting debts for so long,

00:35:05.120 --> 00:35:06.800 line:80%
haven't you saved up something nastier?

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:09.460 line:80%
Something that could
make someone die of anger.

00:35:09.680 --> 00:35:10.430 line:80%
Big Brother,

00:35:10.720 --> 00:35:11.950 line:80%
didn't you tell us,

00:35:12.430 --> 00:35:14.640 line:80%
if they owe money and don't pay...

00:35:15.390 --> 00:35:17.240 line:80%
Kick their ass all the way south?

00:35:17.240 --> 00:35:18.120 line:80%
Get him!

00:35:21.200 --> 00:35:21.680 line:80%
The belt.

00:35:21.680 --> 00:35:22.350 line:80%
It's unnecessary.

00:35:22.350 --> 00:35:22.910 line:80%
Come on.

00:35:22.910 --> 00:35:23.710 line:80%
Let's do this.

00:35:23.910 --> 00:35:25.430 line:80%
Come on, show yourself.

00:35:26.680 --> 00:35:27.080 line:80%
Move it over there.

00:35:27.080 --> 00:35:27.540 line:80%
Come on.

00:35:27.870 --> 00:35:28.830 line:80%
-Go.
-Go.

00:35:30.110 --> 00:35:30.990 line:80%
Go.

00:35:34.080 --> 00:35:35.480 line:80%
Look closely, everyone!

00:35:36.800 --> 00:35:38.600 line:80%
If you don't bring salt and meat,

00:35:39.310 --> 00:35:41.430 line:80%
I'll strip your Heir Apparent naked!

00:35:41.740 --> 00:35:43.800 line:80%
A warrior can be killed
but not humiliated!

00:35:43.800 --> 00:35:44.910 line:80%
I'm really going to strip him!

00:35:44.910 --> 00:35:47.760 line:80%
This is the Marquis of Wu'an's strategy
to lure the enemy?

00:35:47.760 --> 00:35:48.600 line:80%
Wait.

00:35:49.350 --> 00:35:50.720 line:80%
Just wait a bit longer.

00:35:52.030 --> 00:35:53.870 line:80%
If you don't bring salt and meat,

00:35:54.600 --> 00:35:56.730 line:80%
we'll strip your Heir Apparent naked!

00:35:57.720 --> 00:35:58.510 line:80%
Hurry up!

00:35:58.510 --> 00:35:59.910 line:80%
I'm really doing it!

00:36:08.450 --> 00:36:09.780 line:80%
If you don't bring them,

00:36:10.280 --> 00:36:12.880 line:80%
your Heir Apparent
won't have an heir anymore!

00:36:25.810 --> 00:36:26.700 line:80%
Stop!

00:36:31.310 --> 00:36:32.970 line:80%
We'll do it.

00:36:36.430 --> 00:36:37.310 line:80%
General!

00:36:37.870 --> 00:36:38.640 line:80%
General!

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:40.910 line:80%
Greetings, General.

00:36:40.910 --> 00:36:44.040 line:80%
General Shi Yue ordered us
to deliver the meat and grain.

00:36:46.470 --> 00:36:47.790 line:80%
What a coward.

00:36:48.640 --> 00:36:49.800 line:80%
Do as they say!

00:36:57.600 --> 00:36:59.260 line:80%
Don't hurt our Heir Apparent!

00:36:59.310 --> 00:37:00.680 line:80%
Put the stuff in the basket.

00:37:00.680 --> 00:37:01.910 line:80%
Don't try any tricks.

00:37:05.030 --> 00:37:05.640 line:80%
Hurry.

00:37:41.470 --> 00:37:42.510 line:80%
A full basket.

00:37:45.430 --> 00:37:46.080 line:80%
Here.

00:37:47.430 --> 00:37:48.870 line:80%
Don't worry about me!

00:37:48.870 --> 00:37:50.310 line:80%
Xie Zheng isn't here!

00:37:50.310 --> 00:37:52.240 line:80%
Kill these lowlifes for me!

00:37:52.240 --> 00:37:53.640 line:80%
The Heir Apparent has ordered.

00:37:53.640 --> 00:37:54.870 line:80%
Kill!

00:37:54.950 --> 00:37:58.640 line:80%
Kill!

00:38:05.560 --> 00:38:06.510 line:80%
Kill them!

00:38:21.830 --> 00:38:22.710 line:80%
Yes!

00:38:22.760 --> 00:38:24.600 line:80%
-We have food.
-We have provisions, bros.

00:38:24.600 --> 00:38:24.960 line:80%
Yeah!

00:38:24.990 --> 00:38:26.010 line:80%
We won.

00:38:27.550 --> 00:38:28.290 line:80%
Let's go! Let's go!

00:38:28.290 --> 00:38:29.170 line:80%
Okay.

00:38:30.240 --> 00:38:31.600 line:80%
We're back.

00:38:31.600 --> 00:38:32.460 line:80%
We're back.

00:38:32.910 --> 00:38:33.820 line:80%
Great!

00:38:34.600 --> 00:38:35.280 line:80%
Look.

00:38:36.370 --> 00:38:36.830 line:80%
Look at this.

00:38:36.830 --> 00:38:38.320 line:80%
Take these 30 roasted sheep,

00:38:38.320 --> 00:38:46.330 line:80%
[Oil]

00:38:38.640 --> 00:38:40.350 line:80%
50 dan of grain, 50 jin of salt,

00:38:40.350 --> 00:38:41.310 line:80%
and 3 barrels of oil

00:38:41.310 --> 00:38:42.560 line:80%
to the Mess Crew.

00:38:42.990 --> 00:38:44.010 line:80%
Let everyone have a feast!

00:38:44.010 --> 00:38:44.970 line:80%
Great!

00:38:45.470 --> 00:38:46.830 line:80%
Fan is awesome!

00:38:46.960 --> 00:38:49.250 line:80%
More food!

00:38:49.840 --> 00:38:51.040 line:80%
We're having a feast!

00:38:51.940 --> 00:38:52.860 line:80%
[Oil]

00:38:53.480 --> 00:38:55.340 line:80%
[Oil]

00:39:01.760 --> 00:39:03.280 line:80%
We did something big again.

00:39:03.280 --> 00:39:05.280 line:80%
Will the Marquis of Wu'an reward us again?

00:39:05.280 --> 00:39:07.350 line:80%
I only want to ask the Marquis of Wu'an
for one thing.

00:39:07.350 --> 00:39:09.200 line:80%
After we repel the enemy,

00:39:09.310 --> 00:39:11.370 line:80%
hand over that dog Sui Yuanqing to us.

00:39:11.390 --> 00:39:13.320 line:80%
Let us do whatever we want with him.

00:39:13.350 --> 00:39:14.120 line:80%
Good!

00:39:14.240 --> 00:39:15.800 line:80%
That's a good idea. Let's ask together.

00:39:15.800 --> 00:39:16.910 line:80%
Let's do it.

00:39:18.430 --> 00:39:19.390 line:80%
General Wu.

00:39:19.870 --> 00:39:22.280 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing
was exchanged for a lot of food.

00:39:22.280 --> 00:39:23.340 line:80%
Where is Yan Zheng?

00:39:23.510 --> 00:39:25.510 line:80%
There's lamb to help him recover.

00:39:26.470 --> 00:39:28.670 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, His Lordship wants to see you.

00:39:30.200 --> 00:39:31.910 line:80%
His Lordship wants to see us so soon?

00:39:31.910 --> 00:39:33.310 line:80%
What? Is there a reward?

00:39:34.870 --> 00:39:36.530 line:80%
Hand over your weapons first.

00:39:41.080 --> 00:39:42.670 line:80%
Why do we have to hand over our weapons?

00:39:42.670 --> 00:39:44.600 line:80%
No weapons are allowed in the tent.

00:39:47.990 --> 00:39:48.470 line:80%
Here.

00:39:52.800 --> 00:39:54.030 line:80%
What's going on?

00:39:54.080 --> 00:39:55.200 line:80%
Where is Yan Zheng?

00:39:56.280 --> 00:39:57.600 line:80%
After you see His Lordship,

00:39:57.600 --> 00:39:58.720 line:80%
you will see him.

00:40:15.510 --> 00:40:18.370 line:80%
Your Lordship,
Fan Changyu and the others are here.

00:40:20.280 --> 00:40:21.600 line:80%
I am Fan Changyu.

00:40:21.720 --> 00:40:23.250 line:80%
Greetings,
Your Lordship.

00:40:23.310 --> 00:40:24.840 line:80%
Greetings,
Your Lordship.

00:40:29.470 --> 00:40:30.350 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:40:31.030 --> 00:40:32.680 line:80%
You acted without permission.

00:40:32.680 --> 00:40:34.540 line:80%
According to the military rules,

00:40:34.680 --> 00:40:36.540 line:80%
you should be severely punished.

00:40:39.680 --> 00:40:40.210 line:80%
We act...

00:40:40.470 --> 00:40:41.730 line:80%
Acted without orders?

00:40:42.160 --> 00:40:42.910 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:40:42.910 --> 00:40:44.840 line:80%
although we acted without orders,

00:40:45.160 --> 00:40:46.560 line:80%
we also made a contribution.

00:40:46.560 --> 00:40:48.690 line:80%
Please consider this, Your Lordship.

00:40:49.830 --> 00:40:51.950 line:80%
Since you are in the military camp,

00:40:52.120 --> 00:40:54.170 line:80%
you must follow military rules.

00:40:54.510 --> 00:40:57.160 line:80%
If I don't punish
your unauthorized action today,

00:40:57.160 --> 00:40:59.890 line:80%
you will only make
bigger mistakes in the future.

00:41:02.870 --> 00:41:03.640 line:80%
Fine!

00:41:03.800 --> 00:41:05.430 line:80%
Then punish me alone!

00:41:05.680 --> 00:41:07.310 line:80%
I forced them to do it!

00:41:07.680 --> 00:41:08.640 line:80%
No one forced us.

00:41:08.640 --> 00:41:09.510 line:80%
We did it voluntarily!

00:41:09.510 --> 00:41:11.120 line:80%
If there is a punishment,
we take it together.

00:41:11.120 --> 00:41:11.640 line:80%
That's right!

00:41:11.640 --> 00:41:12.310 line:80%
Yes!

00:41:12.310 --> 00:41:15.110 line:80%
Your Lordship,
we clearly earned military merit.

00:41:15.720 --> 00:41:17.560 line:80%
Fan Changyu was determined to get meat

00:41:17.560 --> 00:41:19.420 line:80%
to nourish the wounded soldiers.

00:41:20.030 --> 00:41:21.350 line:80%
Please consider this, Your Lordship.

00:41:21.350 --> 00:41:25.750 line:80%
-Please consider this, Your Lordship.
-Please consider this, Your Lordship.

00:41:30.030 --> 00:41:30.890 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:41:36.280 --> 00:41:38.470 line:80%
Yan Zheng implores Your Lordship again.

00:41:38.470 --> 00:41:39.800 line:80%
Fan Changyu is my wife.

00:41:40.390 --> 00:41:41.720 line:80%
If she is to be punished,

00:41:41.870 --> 00:41:43.160 line:80%
I will bear it with her.

00:41:43.600 --> 00:41:44.640 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:41:44.640 --> 00:41:45.680 line:80%
You are injured.

00:41:45.870 --> 00:41:47.070 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.

00:41:49.680 --> 00:41:52.310 line:80%
According to article 27
of the military regulations,

00:41:52.310 --> 00:41:54.720 line:80%
how much should one be punished

00:41:55.430 --> 00:41:56.680 line:80%
for acting without orders?

00:41:56.680 --> 00:41:58.030 line:80%
Thirty flogs.

00:42:01.640 --> 00:42:04.470 line:80%
Considering Fan Changyu's merit
in breaking the dam,

00:42:04.470 --> 00:42:05.800 line:80%
her righteousness in transporting grain,

00:42:05.800 --> 00:42:07.430 line:80%
and that it is her first offense,

00:42:07.430 --> 00:42:08.680 line:80%
the penalty shall be 20 strokes

00:42:08.680 --> 00:42:09.940 line:80%
as a warning to others.

00:42:10.030 --> 00:42:10.950 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:42:11.720 --> 00:42:12.600 line:80%
please allow me

00:42:13.350 --> 00:42:15.280 line:80%
to be punished on behalf of my wife.

00:42:19.240 --> 00:42:20.760 line:80%
No! No!

00:42:20.760 --> 00:42:21.470 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:42:21.470 --> 00:42:22.990 line:80%
I'll take responsibility
for my own actions.

00:42:22.990 --> 00:42:24.390 line:80%
Just punish me alone.

00:42:24.390 --> 00:42:26.650 line:80%
Please grant my request, Your Lordship.

00:42:27.740 --> 00:42:29.250 line:80%
I... I...

00:42:30.680 --> 00:42:32.540 line:80%
Your Lordship, I know I was wrong.

00:42:33.280 --> 00:42:35.560 line:80%
My husband knows nothing about this.

00:42:35.560 --> 00:42:36.890 line:80%
Please punish me alone!

00:42:36.910 --> 00:42:38.910 line:80%
Th-Then tell me what I should do.

00:42:38.910 --> 00:42:40.440 line:80%
Your Lordship should know,

00:42:40.870 --> 00:42:42.600 line:80%
military orders are absolute.

00:42:42.680 --> 00:42:44.940 line:80%
Disobeying orders is a capital offense.

00:42:51.120 --> 00:42:53.120 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
should be fair in rewards and punishments.

00:42:53.120 --> 00:42:54.510 line:80%
Please give the order, Your Lordship.

00:42:54.510 --> 00:42:55.600 line:80%
Punish only me.

00:42:56.310 --> 00:42:57.600 line:80%
Your Lordship, punish me.

00:42:57.600 --> 00:42:59.120 line:80%
Your Lordship, punish us together.

00:42:59.120 --> 00:42:59.600 line:80%
Punish us together.

00:42:59.600 --> 00:43:00.560 line:80%
Yes, we will take the punishment too.

00:43:00.560 --> 00:43:01.430 line:80%
Punish us together.

00:43:01.430 --> 00:43:02.890 line:80%
Military law is absolute.

00:43:02.950 --> 00:43:03.950 line:80%
This is not a game.

00:43:08.510 --> 00:43:09.370 line:80%
Your Lordship!

00:43:10.080 --> 00:43:10.940 line:80%
Give the order!

00:43:15.910 --> 00:43:18.280 line:80%
This isn't what we discussed.

00:43:19.160 --> 00:43:19.830 line:80%
Men!

00:43:19.830 --> 00:43:20.470 line:80%
Here!

00:43:20.910 --> 00:43:22.680 line:80%
Execute the punishment on Yan Zheng alone.

00:43:22.680 --> 00:43:23.390 line:80%
Yes, Sir.

00:43:23.750 --> 00:43:24.200 line:80%
No!

00:43:24.200 --> 00:43:24.680 line:80%
Proceed!

00:43:24.680 --> 00:43:25.310 line:80%
Your Lordship!

00:43:25.310 --> 00:43:27.040 line:80%
My husband really didn't know.

00:43:29.560 --> 00:43:30.200 line:80%
Your Lordship!

00:43:30.200 --> 00:43:30.830 line:80%
Get away!